reviewText: I have all of these already. They are called (Angels in Disguise). All they did was change the cover and the name on the movie, and selling it as if it is a new item. But it isn't. Now I have two of them.
Very well done and better than I expected. I enjoyed watching this very much! Interesting accounts of Angel encounters.
It was damaged, but I didn't discover that until it was too late to return it.

If you've ever been on the receiving end of a miracle, it's easy to believe that angels exist. Interviewing a variety of people who claim that their lives have been touched by undeniably divine forces, this fascinating program recounts incredible stories in which tragedy, sickness, pain and suffering were alleviated by an inspirational messenger.
